_______________________________________________________________________________
"Psychic Reserve"   
        This gives the Psionicist a 7th stat representing his inner
        mind.  The stat maxes at 12 points.  Each point provides a
        psychic reserve of 25 SP.  These points can be
        withdrawn into regular sp for power casting purposes, but not
        over the psionicist's normal sp limit.  The reserve does not
        regenerate over time, and must be replenished at a cost of 2
        SP per 1 reserve point replaced.  Each and every
        increase of the psychic reserve takes 1 purchase point.
        Psychic Reserve cannot be 'forgotten' once learned.
 
SP Cost:  2 per point	Guild Level:  5		Potential Points:  1
 
Command:  reserve <store/withdraw>
